=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex17 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 200 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 200.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: 23.7357
  harmonic_regularity: 0.7825
  pitch_clarity: 60.8799
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -9.0377
  resonance_freq: 1098.1934

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 17
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 17 ---
{ Klang.ar(`[ [800, 1000, 1200],[0.3, 0.3, 0.3],[pi,pi,pi]], 1, 0) * 0.4}.play;

{ Klang.ar(`[ {exprand(400, 2000)}.dup(16), nil, nil ], 1, 0) * 0.04 }.play;
